<p>(b)  JUA 27/02/2014 Case No. BRA 2/2014 State Reply: 28/04/2014 <b>Alleged ongoing 
</b></p>
<p><b>acts of torture against and killings of prisoners as well as detention conditions in 
</b></p>
<p><b>violation of international human rights law. </b> 
